{"tid":1446602,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］和理優 • 極急召集","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:23:28.000Z","uid":69419,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"15053c072b74284542f050456cd1db93241a47f9","tid":1446602,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"警狗轉晒部署，街頭抗爭成本愈來愈高，前線比人點相，警狗有跟蹤名單，就算升級，係人暗我明既情況之下只會愈趨不利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">（一）罷交稅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n市民要升級首先一定係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷交税！</span></span><br />\n而罷交有一千種方法，不停收唔到張稅單，不停叫稅局重新檢視自己交稅金額。<br />\n一個唔交，最多罰款。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但全港唔交，佢可以做到乜？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">（二）告班狗鬼煽動他人犯罪</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家有狗大聲夾惡扮示威者，大條道理砌低你，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係以為無代價呀嗎？</span></span>之前做過既所有升級，都入晒班狗數，唔使真，只需要有sound bite，更加唔使証據。務求令到班中間派判官，即係懶係眾人皆醉我獨醒個班，相信大部份既升級都係黑警所做既。咩放火、掟磚、衝政府行政大樓個啲，全撚部入佢地數！<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣組唔該。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">（三）搵盡一切證據，將警黑勾結擺上庭審</span></span><br />\n<br />\n只要佢地繼續犯錯，我地死咬唔放。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定可以反敗為勝！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">和理非全面進場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">民間記招同民間調查繼續</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外國關注線路繼續。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">劍盾變陣！</span></span><br />\n你再派多十個二哥上場都唔夠真理同正義打！<br />\n一於同佢個仆街政府戰鬥到底！<br />\n<br />\n<code>不割蓆，不篤灰，不指責，不分化！</code><br />\n<code>光復香港，時代革命！</code>"},{"pid":"419b622af99f95226d5648f2babeb08846aaaf21","tid":1446602,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:08:59.000Z","msg":"push 10次"},{"pid":"55dc6105ba0586d96e54b51e5ea11449fa9987cb","tid":1446602,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b10b7945a327d66fb553219febbf0f6ecc95810","tid":1446602,"uid":111694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:56.000Z","msg":"原來所有衝擊、放火、掟磚 <br />\n全部都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n<br />\n想呃OT錢，自己做埋大龍鳳，唔怪得成個社會立立亂，原來係警察覺編自導自演"},{"pid":"b57c408e91da3dc27feb7349e997136771940dd7","tid":1446602,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d67fdc24d5bbf6602dcc69f305117ce6c6932101","tid":1446602,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dbcc7500ea8f6c1e84067bc902ea18bb71b5c266","tid":1446602,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b10b7945a327d66fb553219febbf0f6ecc95810","tid":1446602,"uid":111694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:56.000Z","msg":"原來所有衝擊、放火、掟磚 <br />\n全部都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n<br />\n想呃OT錢，自己做埋大龍鳳，唔怪得成個社會立立亂，原來係警察覺編自導自演"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"屌,唔撚怪得, 示威者冇汽油彈, 中共都話有<br />\n原來係狗鬼標配"},{"pid":"69190fc1814a237f60376ce349cd01deacb880e2","tid":1446602,"uid":300697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b10b7945a327d66fb553219febbf0f6ecc95810","tid":1446602,"uid":111694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:56.000Z","msg":"原來所有衝擊、放火、掟磚 <br />\n全部都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n<br />\n想呃OT錢，自己做埋大龍鳳，唔怪得成個社會立立亂，原來係警察覺編自導自演"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:22:29.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"91e87cf5c3aec6f03704064eb244408ad1bc7fbe","tid":1446602,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:26:28.000Z","msg"